{"tid":705743,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大角嘴新盤】利奧坊•凱岸加推加價3%   193呎劏房賣499萬","createTime":"2018-06-17T12:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T03:59:20.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"04f3ba01c1826aba6424d6e88b78e96f4e8ff97b","tid":705743,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"【大角嘴新盤】利奧坊&bull;凱岸加推加價3%   193呎劏房賣499萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180617/large/1529232188_9d4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180617%2Flarge%2F1529232188_9d4c.jpg&h=ce8dc66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新盤市況熾熱，恒基（012）大角嘴利奧坊&bull;凱岸上載價單第5號，加推80伙，包括25伙開放式、45伙1房戶、10伙2房戶。<br />\n<br />\n定價由525.1萬元至1,234.4萬元，呎價則由25,264元至32,477元，提供最高折扣優惠5%，折實價由498.8萬元至1.172.7萬元，折實呎價由24,000元至30,853元，定價平均加約3%，是批80伙折實市值逾6億元。是次入場單位為1座6樓L室，實用面積193方呎開放戶，折實價498.8萬元，呎價25,847元。預計最快下周末發售第三輪單位。<br />\n<br />\n另外，同系何文田加多利軒同樣熱賣今天單日連沽6伙，單日套現近半億，或考慮提價加推。"},{"pid":"ab1aad31fd51e229c15f203900db24e9e41e2ff8","tid":705743,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52f9eaebd3f3219dc22c07ee91c5c7c32ccfdb0","tid":705743,"uid":147097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"抵買<br />\n<br />\n證明剛需強勁"},{"pid":"e23828a0e5fd7ba92b363db9ce0ccc32332b4478","tid":705743,"uid":122377,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab1aad31fd51e229c15f203900db24e9e41e2ff8","tid":705743,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"聽日唔買 下次又貴3%"},{"pid":"4970